description:
A DLC pack for GROOVE COASTER WAI WAI PARTY!!!! that includes 10 songs, navigators, and avatars from "maimai DX" and "ONGEKI"!

This pack includes the following content.
■Song Pack (10 songs)
 - VERTeX / Hiro
 - Aiolos / xi
 - FUKUYADORU OTOYA "TAMAONSEN" / TamaOnSen
 - TEmPTaTiON / Kaneko Chiharu *Locked
 - TSUMUGIBOSHI / Kanon Oguni feat.timao
 - MEGATON BLAST / BlackY vs. Yooh
 - Singularity / technoplanet
 - Elusive Emotes / polysha
 - Magical Panic Adventure / Sakuzyo
 - Island Breeze / Palme

■Navigator
 - Ras *with voice (CV: Sakura Ayane)
 - Hoshizaki Akari *with voice (CV: Akao Hikaru)

■Avatar
 - Ras(2D)
 - Otohime(2D)
 - DXkuma(2D)
 - Hoshizaki Akari(2D)
 - Sumeragi Setsuna(2D)
 - Navi-nyan(2D)

*Some content will be unlocked via missions after downloading.
name: maimai DX + ONGEKI Pack
